  "text": "In all previously commented studies, the training cohort to create the algorithms differed from the validation cohort. This approach precludes correction for interindividual variations like LV and RV anatomy, rotation of the heart, or lead placement, [CITATION_1] which may have also contributed to their limited accuracy to predict the VT SoO. Table 2 summarizes the proposed algorithms to identify the endocardial VT SoO in patients with previous MI.",
